      "lernziele": "<p>Knowledge of the Deep Learning approaches for large data sets and the ability to apply the appropriate algorithm for successfully solving a given machine learning problem.</p>",
      "planinhalt": "<p>&bull; Review Linear Algebra, Probability and Numerical Computation<br />&bull; Machine Learning Basics<br />&bull; Deep Feedforward Networks<br />&bull; Regularization for Deep Learning<br />&bull; Optimization for Training Deep Models<br />&bull; Convolutional Networks<br />&bull; Sequence Modeling<br />&bull; Practical Methodology<br />The module is based on the excellent book: &quot;Deep Learning&quot; from Ian<br />Goodfellow, Yoshua Bengio and Aaron Courville.</p>",
